data.description: 4 Bed, 1 1/2 Bath 1728 Sq. Ft. Split Enty Home on half acre lot in the Heights. Entry way with coat hooks and ceiling fan. Upper level has living room w/picture window, kitchen/dining w/patio door to covered deck, 2 bedrooms and full bath. Daylight lower level features family room, 2 additional bedrooms and ½ bath/laundry combo room with garage and backyard access.  Washer/Dryer stay. Oversized double attached garage w/bonus space.  Detached shop w/overhead door.  Well for watering lawn.
